# Mosquitto ACL (Access Control List) Configuration Example
#
# Format:
#   user <username>
#   topic [read|write|readwrite] <topic>
#
# Wildcards:
#   + matches single level
#   # matches multiple levels
#
# To use:
# 1. Copy to 'acl.conf' (remove .example)
# 2. Uncomment acl_file line in mosquitto.conf
# 3. Restart broker

# ==============================================
# VanDaemon Backend Service
# ==============================================
user vandaemon
topic readwrite vandaemon/#

# ==============================================
# LED Dimmer Devices
# ==============================================
user leddimmer
topic read vandaemon/leddimmer/+/channel/+/set
topic read vandaemon/leddimmer/+/all/set
topic write vandaemon/leddimmer/+/channel/+/state
topic write vandaemon/leddimmer/+/status
topic write vandaemon/leddimmer/+/config
topic write vandaemon/leddimmer/+/heartbeat

# ==============================================
# Anonymous Users (if allow_anonymous is true)
# ==============================================
# Allow read-only access to state topics
user anonymous
topic read vandaemon/#
